user.biography:
Oh, to be a mad, mouthy, majestic woman 
in a world full of frauds and followers…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brittany Renner in Dallas, Texas with @mahamaarouf_. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: The best thing about memories is making them @mahamaarouf_ 🧡💙

node.text:
Walking for @ellaelisque was absolutely MAGICAL! Thank you for the opportunity @maxiejofficial, you are a true visionary 🤩 You put together an incredible group of people to bring life to an event that I will never forget. 

I really appreciate everyone who continues to support me. One thing about me…I don’t bend, I don’t break, I STAND 💪🏽

(I got so hype when I saw @blameitonkway gassing me 😍 twinkletoes 🩰🧚🏽‍♀️😂)

MUA: @alexjairus 
Hair: @seanchristopherfears 
Video cred: @glennspin
